{"tid":2062413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【歌已唱】我再搓潤雄  後入他滿肛紅","createTime":"2020-06-13T06:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T16:39:34.000Z","uid":47374,"like":78,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa52e7348aab0f0af8fe3761b8e9136e4b5e2fd","tid":2062413,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:12:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-525932743/ndxy1im0dcub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-525932743%2Fndxy1im0dcub&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJriC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=7e586f19\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-525932743/ndxy1im0dcub</a><br />\n<br />\n我再搓潤雄 後入他滿肛紅<br />\n這晚上憑著愛把陰莖蠕動<br />\n<br />\n我愛撫潤雄 被肉體再牽動<br />\n這愛液隨著那春風 射滿肛中<br />\n然而我越插越激動<br />\n這千古抑壓怎形容<br />\n精子無窮 陰莖失控"},{"pid":"a133ac5809538c5472895c887193420a0b675e7a","tid":2062413,"uid":4158,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你點寫的"},{"pid":"ec78e19e55a1f030af69028248ad4bef27eb56f1","tid":2062413,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:20:03.000Z","msg":"好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d31803b461a40f249961fbf90c41f1ea99c98f2","tid":2062413,"uid":47374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a133ac5809538c5472895c887193420a0b675e7a","tid":2062413,"uid":4158,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你點寫的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"屌過佢就ok"},{"pid":"b07ff7d4cac18a10b67d6cfd5e57673fd6c02834","tid":2062413,"uid":72045,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"入黎冇睇名, 一聽把聲就知係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla